PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2000, No. 4, LIARD FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on specified tracts of land in the Yukon, until March 31, 2002, and (b) repeals the Prohibition of Entry on Certain Lands Order, No. 8 of 1996.
